Name: The Rose & Lily
Description:
Give them a bouquet they’ll never forget. This bountiful display brings together a tasteful, luxurious collaboration of oriental lilies, white and pink roses, supported by a healthy portion of green bell. Hand-wrapped in two sheets of frosted cellophane, this bouquet has been carefully arranged by our expert florists.


Bouquet Details:     
• 2 x White Oriental Lily
• 4 x White Rose
• 4 x Pink Rose
• 2 x Green Bell
• Wrapped in frosted cellophane.  
• Stem length: Aprox. 50cm  
Hand-tied by our florists. 
Please note the vase is not included.    

Our flowers may arrive unopened but the buds will come into bloom within a day or two.

In the rare event that a substitution is necessary through flower supply difficulties, we may substitute with flowers of similar or superior style, quality and value. Warning: this bouquet contains lilies, which are poisonous to cats and dogs. Please ensure to keep your bouquet away from any pets.

Our Commitment to Quality:

From blossom to bouquet, every step of your flowers’ journey is handled with care to ensure long-lasting, beautiful blooms. That means:

  • Five days of freshness guaranteed or we’ll replace your flowers
  • Each bouquet is hand-tied by our florists
  • Flowers arrive ‘in bud’ to preserve freshness
  • Guard petals protect roses in transit
  • Bouquets come in our signature Nourishing Wrap to keep them happy while travelling
  • Next day delivery with full SMS tracking and a two hour delivery window
